N2  - The article presents notes about persons and places associated with the Academy of Management. Donald G. Halper has been appointed to serve as the chairman of the Department of Management and Marketing at Fresno State College. John W. Darr is now Professor and Coordinator of the Internship Program at the Bowling Green State University College of Business Administration. Aly A. Baylor has joined the Department of Business Administration of Texas Western College.
